snippet.title: Vultures Scavengers of Death - Indie Horror Showcase  (October 2024)
snippet.description:
Play the demo and wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2537470/Vultures__Scavengers_of_Death/?utm_source=Indiehorror 

Face down the twisted monsters of a 90's survival game inspired world in this tactical turn-based survival horror. As an operative of VULTURES, scavenge the infested metropolis for materials and information that could cure the infection plaguing the world.

Vultures Scavengers of Death Socials
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2537470/Vultures__Scavengers_of_Death/?utm_source=Indiehorror 
Website: https://vulturesgame.com/
Discord: https://discord.gg/vsxD6n8P8J  
Twitter: https://x.com/VulturesGame

Trailer maker: Firesquid
